-black\">AF</span><span class=\"hidden sm:inline\">AlgoForge</span></a><nav class=\"hidden lg:flex items-center gap-1\" aria-label=\"Main\"><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/problems\">Problems</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/topics\">Topics</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/patterns\">Patterns</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/roadmaps\">Roadmaps</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/blind-75\">Blind 75</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/companies\">Companies</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a></nav></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><a class=\"hidden sm:inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card px-3 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:border-primary/40 transition-colors\" href=\"/search\"><span>Search…</span><kbd class=\"rounded border border-border bg-muted px-1.5 text-[10px] font-mono\">/</kbd></a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/dashboard\">Progress</a><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 hover:bg-muted text-foreground h-9 w-9\" aria-label=\"Toggle theme\"></button></div></div></header><main id=\"main\" class=\"min-h-[70vh]\"><div class=\"container-af py-10\"><nav aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\" class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://algoforge.dev/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Problems\",\"item\":\"https://algoforge.dev/problems\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Index Pairs of a String\",\"item\":\"https://algoforge.dev/problems/index-pairs-of-a-string\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":4,\"name\":\"C++\",\"item\":\"https://algoforge.dev/problems/index-pairs-of-a-string/cpp\"}]}</script><ol class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-1.5\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><a class=\"hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"text-border\">/</span><a class=\"hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/problems\">Problems</a></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"text-border\">/</span><a class=\"hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/problems/index-pairs-of-a-string\">Index Pairs of a String</a></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"text-border\">/</span><span class=\"text-foreground font-medium\" aria-current=\"page\">C++</span></li></ol></nav><div class=\"mt-4 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide bg-easy/15 text-easy\">Easy</span></div><h1 class=\"mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight\">Index Pairs of a String<!-- --> — <!-- -->C++</h1><p class=\"mt-2 text-muted-foreground\"><a class=\"text-primary hover:underline\" href=\"/problems/index-pairs-of-a-string\">Full explanation</a> · <!-- -->Time <!-- -->O(n + m + z)<!-- --> · Space <!-- -->O(t)</p><div class=\"mt-8\"><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-border overflow-hidden bg-code-bg text-slate-100\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-2 border-b border-white/10 bg-black/30 px-2 py-1.5\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-1\" role=\"tablist\" aria-label=\"Language\"><button role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"true\" class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-medium transition-colors bg-white/15 text-white\">C++</button><button role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-medium transition-colors text-slate-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5\">Python</button></div><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 px-3 text-sm text-slate-300 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/10 h-8\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Copy code\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-copy h-3.5 w-3.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"14\" height=\"14\" x=\"8\" y=\"8\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2\"></path></svg>Copy</button></div><pre class=\"overflow-x-auto p-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed font-mono max-h-[32rem]\"><code>// Time:  O(n + m + z), n is the total size of patterns\n//                    , m is the total size of query string\n//                    , z is the number of all matched strings\n// Space: O(t), t is the total size of ac automata trie\n\nstruct AhoNode {\n    vector&lt;AhoNode *&gt; children;\n    vector&lt;int&gt; indices;\n    AhoNode *suffix;\n    AhoNode *output;\n    AhoNode() :\n        children(26, nullptr),\n        suffix(nullptr),\n        output(nullptr) {}\n};\n\nclass AhoTrie {\npublic:\n    AhoTrie(const vector&lt;string&gt;&amp; patterns) : root_(createACTrie(patterns)) {\n        node_ = createACSuffixAndOutputLinks(root_);\n    }\n\n    vector&lt;int&gt; step(char letter) {\n        while (node_ &amp;&amp; !node_-&gt;children[letter - &#x27;a&#x27;]) {\n            node_ = node_-&gt;suffix;\n        }\n        node_ = node_ ? node_-&gt;children[letter - &#x27;a&#x27;] : root_;\n        return getACNodeOutputs(node_);\n    }\n\nprivate:\n    AhoNode *createACTrie(const vector&lt;string&gt;&amp; patterns) {  // Time:  O(n), Space: O(t)\n        auto root = new AhoNode();\n        for (int i = 0; i &lt; patterns.size(); ++i) {\n            auto node = root;\n            for (const auto&amp; c : patterns[i]) {\n                if (!node-&gt;children[c - &#x27;a&#x27;]) {\n                    node-&gt;children[c - &#x27;a&#x27;] = new AhoNode();\n                }\n                node = node-&gt;children[c - &#x27;a&#x27;];\n            }\n            node-&gt;indices.emplace_back(i);\n        }\n        return root;\n    }\n    \n    AhoNode *createACSuffixAndOutputLinks(AhoNode *root) {  // Time:  O(n), Space: O(t)\n        queue&lt;AhoNode *&gt; q;\n        for (auto node : root-&gt;children) {\n            if (!node) {\n                continue;\n            }\n            q.emplace(node);\n            node-&gt;suffix = root;\n        }\n                \n        while (!q.empty()) {\n            auto node = q.front(); q.pop();\n            for (int c = 0; c &lt; node-&gt;children.size(); ++c) {\n                if (!node-&gt;children[c]) {\n                    continue;\n                }\n                auto child = node-&gt;children[c];\n                q.emplace(child);\n                auto suffix = node-&gt;suffix;\n                while (suffix &amp;&amp; !suffix-&gt;children[c]) {\n                    suffix = suffix-&gt;suffix;\n                }\n                child-&gt;suffix = suffix ? suffix-&gt;children[c] : root;\n                child-&gt;output = !child-&gt;suffix-&gt;indices.empty() ?\n                    child-&gt;suffix : child-&gt;suffix-&gt;output;\n            }\n        }\n        \n        return root;\n    }\n    \n    vector&lt;int&gt; getACNodeOutputs(AhoNode *node) {  // Time:  O(z)\n        vector&lt;int&gt; result;\n        for (const auto&amp; i : node_-&gt;indices) {\n            result.emplace_back(i);\n            // return result;\n        }\n        auto output = node_-&gt;output;\n        while (output) {\n            for (const auto&amp; i : output-&gt;indices) {\n                result.emplace_back(i);\n                // return result;\n            }\n            output = output-&gt;output;\n        }\n        return result;\n    }\n    \n    AhoNode * const root_;\n    AhoNode *node_;\n};\n\nclass Solution {\npublic:\n    vector&lt;vector&lt;int&gt;&gt; indexPairs(string text, vector&lt;string&gt;&amp; words) {\n        for (auto&amp; word : words) {\n            reverse(word.begin(), word.end());\n        }\n        AhoTrie trie(words);\n        vector&lt;vector&lt;int&gt;&gt; result;\n        for (int i = text.length() - 1; i &gt;= 0; --i) {\n            for (const auto&amp; j : trie.step(text[i])) {\n                result.push_back({i, i + words[j].length() - 1});\n            }\n        }\n        reverse(result.begin(), result.end());\n        return result;\n    }\n};\n</code></pre></div></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"mt-20 border-t border-border bg-sidebar\"><div class=\"container-af py-12 grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4\"><div><p class=\"font-bold text-lg\">AlgoForge</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground max-w-xs\">Master coding interviews with patterns, roadmaps, and solutions</p></div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-sm mb-3\">Learn</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/problems\">Problems</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/patterns\">Patterns</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/roadmaps\">Roadmaps</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/blind-75\">Blind 75</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/grind-169\">Grind 169</a></li></ul></div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-sm mb-3\">Interview</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/companies\">Companies</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/interview-preparation\">Interview prep</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/system-design\">System design</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/glossary\">Glossary</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a></li></ul></div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-sm mb-3\">Product</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/pricing\">Pricing</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/about\">About</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/about/attribution\">Attribution</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/sitemap-html\">Sitemap</a></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"border-t border-border\"><div class=\"container-af py-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-2 justify-between text-xs text-muted-foreground\"><p>© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> <!-- -->AlgoForge<!-- -->. Educational use only.</p><p>Solution code sourced under MIT from<!-- --> <a href=\"https://github.com/kamyu104/LeetCode-Solutions\" class=\"underline hover:text-primary\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">kamyu104/LeetCode-Solutions</a>. Explanations are original AlgoForge content.</p></div></div></footer><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/05kafvajig4wu.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[427423,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/2fvm6eoqeukxu